extends layout

block content
  div.header(style="background:rgb(81,192,102);")
    a(href="/")
      img.barLogo(src="/images/shareServeBigWhite.png")
    div(style="margin-right:auto;margin-left:12px;")
      div(style="font-size:45px;") ShareServe 
      div(style="font-size:30px;font-style:italic;") A Community-Based Server Marketplace
    a.userContainer(href="/user/dashboard/" style="text-decoration:none;color:white;")
      div(style="font-size:25px;") jpwall
      img(src="/images/downArrow.png" style="width:40px;height:40px")
  div.progressBar
    div.progressStep.homeInfoText(style="background:rgb(186,109,255)") Step 1: Select Server Type
    div.progressStep.homeInfoText Step 2: Customize Server Information
    div.progressStep.homeInfoText Step 3: Availability
  form.newListingItemContainer
    a.newListingItem(href="/newHomeServer" style="justify-content: space-around;text-decoration:none;width:100%;padding-left:15%;padding-right:15%;")
      input(type="radio" style="width: 2%;display:none;" name="serverType")
      div(style="width: 95%;")
        div.homeTitleText Home Server
        div.homeInfoText(style="color:white;") Choose this server setup if you have configured a home computer to act as a server. This typically applies to most desktops and laptops or servers that do not fall into the other categories.
    a.newListingItem(href="/newPerformanceServer" style="justify-content: space-around;text-decoration:none;width:100%;padding-left:15%;padding-right:15%;")
      input(type="radio" style="width: 2%;display:none;" name="serverType")
      div(style="width: 95%;")
        div.homeTitleText High Performance Server
        div.homeInfoText(style="color:white;") A high performance server typically contains a large amount of RAM, sometimes includes ECC memory, multiple cores per processor or more than one processor on a motherboard, and support for multiple Virtual Machines. 
    a.newListingItem(href="/newGraphicsServer" style="justify-content: space-around;text-decoration:none;width:100%;padding-left:15%;padding-right:15%;")
      input(type="radio" style="width: 2%;display:none;" name="serverType")
      div(style="width: 95%;")
        div.homeTitleText Graphics Server
        div.homeInfoText(style="color:white;") This server type contains a graphics card as well as higher performance hardware that might be necessary for 3D rendering - i.e. a multi-core CPU, large amounts of memory and hard drive space, as well as a suitable Operating System for these tasks. 